00:00:11.040 --> 00:00:15.580
Bruno has been building his own amusement
park in the woods of Italy for the last 40

00:00:15.580 --> 00:00:16.580
years.

00:00:16.580 --> 00:00:21.140
Ai Pioppi is a restaurant in Battaglia, Italy
that he opened in 1969 and when he couldn't

00:00:21.140 --> 00:00:24.820
find a welder to make some hooks that he needed,
he taught himself to weld.

00:00:24.820 --> 00:00:28.840
Bruno started creating these rides to build
surrounding the restaurant and to date they

00:00:28.840 --> 00:00:34.790
include zip lines, roller coasters, tilt a
whirls, swings, and slides for both children

00:00:34.790 --> 00:00:35.799
and adults.

00:00:35.799 --> 00:00:40.120
Kate McGwire makes beautiful sculptures out
of bird feathers such as this one from rooster

00:00:40.120 --> 00:00:45.400
feathers, one made from Mallard feathers,
a combination of dove and swan feathers, and

00:00:45.400 --> 00:00:47.720
this one from crow feathers.

00:00:47.720 --> 00:00:52.549
And she says she likes using well known materials
in an unexpected way to play with the senses.&nbsp;

00:00:52.549 --> 00:00:57.720
Embodying Ethics: Endangered is a project
by Rohan Chhabra where hunting jackets transform

00:00:57.720 --> 00:01:00.170
into animals under attack from illegal poaching.

00:01:00.170 --> 00:01:03.650
And he's hoping to raise awareness for this
issue.

00:01:03.650 --> 00:01:10.920
Some of the jackets include the Saiga Antelope,
Asian Elephant, Gorilla, Rhino, and Tiger.

00:01:10.920 --> 00:01:15.290
Mike Iverson of Blind Squirrel Props creates
incredible weapons, helmets and other props

00:01:15.290 --> 00:01:18.610
from comics, anime, movies and video games.

00:01:18.610 --> 00:01:24.870
Like this Dragon Ball Z Scouter, an AEP7 Laser
Pistol from Fallout, Boromir's Shield from

00:01:24.870 --> 00:01:31.090
Lord of The Rings, a Game of Thrones Dragon
Egg, BPRD Pistol from the Hellboy comic, and

00:01:31.090 --> 00:01:32.650
this submachine gun.

00:01:32.650 --> 00:01:36.870
It comes with step by step directions that
you can download and try yourself.

