00:01:37.870 --> 00:01:41.370
Radiology art was created by physician and
artist Satre Stuelke.

00:01:41.370 --> 00:01:44.950
He made them while in medical school because
he wanted to see the interior structures of

00:01:44.950 --> 00:01:49.770
everyday objects and ultimately hopes to make
it easier for patients to relate to the radiological

00:01:49.770 --> 00:01:51.479
procedures that they go through.

00:01:51.479 --> 00:01:55.159
His works include electronics, toys, and even
food.&nbsp;

00:01:55.159 --> 00:01:58.200
Thoms creates cool cartoon-like street art.

00:01:58.200 --> 00:02:04.210
Some examples of his work include Nerd Power,
My Little Kijo, Right to Housing, and Hair

00:02:04.210 --> 00:02:05.210
cut.

00:02:05.210 --> 00:02:08.470
Check out his website for more great street
art, sculptures, paintings.

00:02:08.470 --> 00:02:26.590
