The Bad Guy art show celebrating Cult Villains...

00:02:26.590 --> 00:02:31.120
Michael Paul Smith creates these scenes with
old cars using forced perspective.

00:02:31.120 --> 00:02:36.370
By setting up tiny model cars and scenes on
card tables he photographs them from the perfect

00:02:36.370 --> 00:02:39.840
angle to seamlessly blend them into the environment.

00:02:39.840 --> 00:02:43.760
He's been creating a fictional small town
he calls Elgin Park.

